# Lab 01 - Basic LAN Connectivity

## Objective
Configure two PCs on the same network and verify communication.

## Topology
PC0 ---- Switch0 ---- PC1


## Configuration

PC0
IP: 192.168.1.10
Mask: 255.255.255.0

PC1
IP: 192.168.1.20
Mask: 255.255.255.0

## Verification

Ping from PC0 to PC1 successful.

## Troubleshooting

Changed PC1 to 192.168.2.20.

Result:
Ping failed because devices were on different networks.

## Lessons Learned

Devices must be in the same subnet to communicate through a Layer 2 switch.
